Body: Description: After applying the scanning the reports are not generated multiple devices
What We've Learned Updated: The issue persist after our remote, where we collected logs.
Next Steps Updated: ADO to be created
Next Steps Updated: ADO to be updated

What We've Learned Updated: The partitions from Ediscovery are time labeled. For example the partition with time label June last year should be selected for the search.

Keep in mind that when a new scan is started all previous scan results are lost. An Audit Log backup for eDiscovery is recommended before starting a new scan. A message with this recommendation is displayed in a popup when starting a new scan.
Next Steps Updated: Inform the customer about how partition are working!
